title: Lou Reed - Live at Montreux 2000
description:
Lou Reed - Live at Montreux 2000

MPEG-4 Nero Digital AVC
NTSC DVD - 29.97 frames per second, recoded accordingly at 29.97 fps
Audio AAC-LC 448 kbps from LPCM 2 channel stereo soundtrack

2 hours

Very entertaining performance from Lou's tour connected with release of his 2000 album, Ecstasy.  It's his only appearance at the Montreux Jazz Festival.
